overview: “Different lives, different stories”  A young woman who enjoys keeping a journal of everything happened to come across her neighbors. Little did they know, it was this girl who knows their secrets. Strangely as it is, the girl herself has her own secrets to unfold.
tagline: Tumahan, magdahan-dahan sa paghakbang tungo sa paglaya ng takot sa isipan.
title: tahandahan
